<li class="slider-item">
<ul class="tashuo-list">
<li class="tashuo-item J-item" data-tashuoId="5274c62669b4fcfb8b4e839c">
<div class="tashuo-author">
<a href="/usercenter/userpage?uk=0287e287&authorId=76f8efb94347c9cf8ffed623&from=lemma" target="_blank">
<div class="ta-author-area"><span><img src="https://imgsa.baidu.com/baike/pic/item/8d5494eef01f3a29f83f52d99625bc315c607c36.jpg" /></span></div>
<div class="ta-author-slogan-area">
<strong>温乎</strong>
<span>读历史、谈世事、阅人物</span>
</div>
<i></i></a>
</div>
<a href="/tashuo/browse/content?id=5274c62669b4fcfb8b4e839c&lemmaId=305344&fromLemmaModule=pcBottom" class="cover" target="_blank">
<img src="https://imgsa.baidu.com/baike/pic/item/d8f9d72a6059252d4df4811c3b9b033b5ab5b9c3.jpg" data-width="" data-height="" class="cover-img">
<div class="overlay"><img src="https://bkssl.bdimg.com/static/wiki-lemma/widget/lemma_content/mainContent/tashuo/img/overlay_543bb29.png"></div>
<p class="title">
《岳阳楼记》今犹在，不见当年范仲淹
</p></a>
<p class="abstract">
<a href="/tashuo/browse/content?id=5274c62669b4fcfb8b4e839c&lemmaId=305344&fromLemmaModule=pcBottom" target="_blank">
一篇《岳阳楼记》，惊艳了时光。

千年来，它早已成为仁人志士的座右铭，

激励着历代英雄豪杰，奋马扬鞭，

鼓舞着无数君子以此为皋镍，

在范仲淹的理想道路上，前赴后继。

“这世界上有两种力量——思想和剑，

而思想总是战胜利剑。”</a>
</p>
<div class="tashuo-operator">
<span class="tashuo-publish-date">2019-09-19</span><span class="tashuo-like J-like tashuo-liked" data-isvote="1"><i></i><strong class="J-number">9</strong></span>
</div>
</li>
<li class="tashuo-item J-item" data-tashuoId="3b693b6b19d5a338ecde467a">
<div class="tashuo-author">
<a href="/usercenter/userpage?uk=1efbdf04&authorId=222bebc5db0a5b24b0bd5e21&from=lemma" target="_blank">
<div class="ta-author-area"><span><img src="https://imgsa.baidu.com/baike/pic/item/6609c93d70cf3bc756fb14c4da00baa1cd112a1b.jpg" /></span></div>
<div class="ta-author-slogan-area">
<strong>写乎</strong>
<span>探究历史悬疑，挖掘地方风物</span>
</div>
<i></i></a>
</div>
<a href="/tashuo/browse/content?id=3b693b6b19d5a338ecde467a&lemmaId=305344&fromLemmaModule=pcBottom" class="cover" target="_blank">
<img src="https://imgsa.baidu.com/baike/pic/item/7c1ed21b0ef41bd509a4febd5fda81cb38db3d87.jpg" data-width="" data-height="" class="cover-img">
<div class="overlay"><img src="https://bkssl.bdimg.com/static/wiki-lemma/widget/lemma_content/mainContent/tashuo/img/overlay_543bb29.png"></div>
<p class="title">
没有登上岳阳楼的范仲淹是怎么写下的《岳阳楼记》？
</p></a>
<p class="abstract">
<a href="/tashuo/browse/content?id=3b693b6b19d5a338ecde467a&lemmaId=305344&fromLemmaModule=pcBottom" target="_blank">
范仲淹本人没有登临过岳阳楼，凭着滕子京寄给他的一张《洞庭秋晚图》，借景喻情，写下了云霞纸上，气势非凡，融注着他忧乐天下的民本思想的传世名篇《岳阳楼记》。滕子京将其刻在了岳阳楼上。</a>
</p>
<div class="tashuo-operator">
<span class="tashuo-publish-date">2019-05-05</span><span class="tashuo-like J-like " data-isvote="0"><i></i><strong class="J-number">246</strong></span>
</div>
</li>
<li class="tashuo-item J-item" data-tashuoId="24921b1a0cc887e07289d9fd">
<div class="tashuo-author">
<a href="/usercenter/userpage?uk=a90bc803&authorId=d276fc8ff126ce5c74e76821&from=lemma" target="_blank">
<div class="ta-author-area"><span><img src="https://imgsa.baidu.com/baike/pic/item/4034970a304e251f9c577536ad86c9177e3e535f.jpg" /></span></div>
<div class="ta-author-slogan-area">
<strong>叶之秋</strong>
<span>专栏作家</span>
</div>
<i></i></a>
</div>
<a href="/tashuo/browse/content?id=24921b1a0cc887e07289d9fd&lemmaId=305344&fromLemmaModule=pcBottom" class="cover" target="_blank">
<img src="https://imgsa.baidu.com/baike/pic/item/6609c93d70cf3bc7ab5e7863dd00baa1cc112ae6.jpg" data-width="" data-height="" class="cover-img">
<div class="overlay"><img src="https://bkssl.bdimg.com/static/wiki-lemma/widget/lemma_content/mainContent/tashuo/img/overlay_543bb29.png"></div>
<p class="title">
范仲淹《岳阳楼记》是在为好友吹嘘？滕子京在岳州究竟做了啥？
</p></a>
<p class="abstract">
<a href="/tashuo/browse/content?id=24921b1a0cc887e07289d9fd&lemmaId=305344&fromLemmaModule=pcBottom" target="_blank">
范仲淹确实是古代难得的君子，他为官为民也颇有情怀。不过，范仲淹并非圣人，并非完人，他身上一样有毛病。并且，在为滕子京写《岳阳楼记》这件事情上，他确实犯了一个不大不小的错误。许多朋友可能对这段历史并不清楚，我简单叙述一下。1、滕子京为何被贬？滕子京，本名滕宗谅，字子京。此人和...</a>
</p>
<div class="tashuo-operator">
<span class="tashuo-publish-date">2018-06-22</span><span class="tashuo-like J-like " data-isvote="0"><i></i><strong class="J-number">187</strong></span>
</div>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul></div>
</div>
